# Done Folder

Completed and processed items (audit trail).

## Example: Completed Email Response

```markdown
---
type: email
from: client@example.com
subject: Invoice Request
received: 2026-03-09T10:30:00Z
completed_at: 2026-03-09T11:15:00Z
processed_by: email_agent
status: completed
---

## Original Request

Can you please send me the invoice for last month?

## Actions Taken

1. Generated invoice #1234 ($500 for February 2026)
2. Replied to client with invoice attached
3. Archived original email

## Attachments Generated

- invoices/2026-02/Invoice_1234.pdf

## Outcome

Client received invoice within 45 minutes of request.
```

